fields.description:
There are performance issues with many security groups and security group rules. We should add database indexes to speed up performance, e.g.

{code}
create index networkrule_id_idx on metadata_network_rule_ip_ranges ( networkrule_id );
create index metadata_network_group_rule_fk_idx on metadata_network_rule ( metadata_network_group_rule_fk );
{code}

and others as appropriate.
